title: SOLO Moody Blues (15 CDs) [olaf]
description:
Solo Moody Blues albums, including:

Graeme Edge Band - 1975 - Kick Off Your Muddy Boots
Graeme Edge Band - 1977 - Paradise Ballroom

John Lodge - 1977 - Natural Avenue

Justin Hayward - 1977 - Songwriter
Justin Hayward - 1980 - Night Flight
Justin Hayward - 1985 - Moving Mountains
Justin Hayward - 1994 - Classic Blue
Justin Hayward - 1996 - The View From The Hill

Justin Hayward & John Lodge - 1975 - Blue Jays

Mike Pinder - 1976 - The Promise
Mike Pinder - 1995 - Among The Stars
Mike Pinder - 1995 - A Planet With One Mind
Mike Pinder - 1996 - A People With One Heart

Ray Thomas - 1975 - From Mighty Oaks
Ray Thomas - 1976 - Hopes Wishes & Dreams

Most tracks 192-320 VBR, some not that good. Enjoy!
